1. *Prstiju* je bilo teško ugrebati led sa vjetrobranskog stakla. (It was hard to scrape the ice off the windshield with *prstiju*.)
2. Uzela je maramicu i obrišila *prstiju* nakon što je pojela pljeskavicu. (She took a napkin and wiped her *prstiju* after eating a burger.)
3. Dok je brojala novac, primijetila je da joj nedostaje jedan novčić između *prstiju*. (While counting the money, she noticed that she was missing one coin between her *prstiju*.)
4. Oštetio je lakat pa je držao ruku savijenu i pridržavao ju drugom *prstiju*. (He injured his elbow, so he kept his arm bent and supported it with his other *prstiju*.)
5. Uradila je manikir i sada je ponosno pokazivala svoje nokte na *prstiju*. (She got a manicure and now proudly showed off her nails on her *prstiju*.)
6. *Prstiju* na nogama su joj bili toliko smrznuti da ih nije osjećala. (Her toes were so frozen that she couldn't feel her *prstiju*.)
7. Dijete je pokušavalo naučiti da broji na *prstiju* i činilo se da mu ide dobro. (The child was trying to learn to count on their *prstiju* and it seemed to be going well.)
8. Pogledao je kroz prozor i primijetio da je *prstiju* snijega napadalo tijekom noći. (He looked out the window and noticed that there was a finger's worth of snow that had fallen overnight.)
9. Nije znala kako da zaveže pertle pa joj je majka pokazala trik s petljom oko palca i kažiprsta, a onda prebacivanjem na drugi *prstiju*. (She didn't know how to tie her shoelaces, so her mother showed her a trick with a loop around her thumb and index finger, and then transfer it to the other *prstiju*.)
10. Čekala je da prođe crveno svjetlo na semaforu, dok su joj se neugodno trljali *prstiju* u hladnoći. (She waited for the red light to turn green at the traffic light, while her fingers uncomfortably rubbed against each other in the cold.)